# SlidePress — Core

Solo-founder marketing automation: topic → carousel slides → AI images → voiceover → captions → zip / narration / MP4 → direct post (YouTube, TikTok, Instagram).

**Live:** [slidepress.co](https://www.slidepress.co) · **Repo name:** `content-engine`

## Philosophy

- **Efficiency:** Minimize DB roundtrips; avoid bloated dependencies.
- **React Compiler:** `reactCompiler: true` — no `useMemo` / `useCallback` / `React.memo` unless external non-React refs.
- **Data integrity:** Zod + TypeScript on every AI payload; schemas must match DB columns.

## Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| App | Next.js App Router, React 19, Tailwind (dark zinc + orange) |
| Host | Vercel |
| DB / auth | Supabase (`@supabase/ssr`, RLS, Realtime) |
| Slide copy + voiceover | Google Gemini 2.5 Flash (JSON + Zod) |
| Images | Fal.ai Nano Banana 2 (async webhooks) |
| TTS / video | ElevenLabs + FFmpeg (Fal) + narration cache |
| Mobile | Capacitor 8 — WebView shell, not React Native |
| Billing | Stripe (web) + RevenueCat (iOS/Android IAP) |

## Layout

- API routes: `app/api/[route]/route.ts`
- Utils: `utils/` (flat, modular)
- Types: `types/`
- Migrations: `supabase/migrations/`
- Internal docs: `docs/` — see `docs/claude-project.md` for AI context

